Localization.Name: Deadrig 'Noxious' Shotgun
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Unknown
Item Type: Shotgun
Class: Ballistic

Magazine Size: 8
Rate Of Fire: 120 rpm
Effective Range: 0-10 m

Attachments: N/A

The Deadrig is a high powered, double-barreled shotgun with a simple design pieced together from junkyard scraps. Prioritizing power above all else, the Deadrig lacks the refinement of mass-produced weapons and suffers from heavy recoil. The Noxious variant features more green coloration due to the scrap metal used during its assembly.
